title: [SOLVED]A1502 no power.
message:
Macbook pro 820-3476 no power

I have 12.58 stable 
ISL6259 acok - 3.40V
Magsafe - Ok
SMC_ADAPTER_EN - 3.40V
PP5V_S5 - 5V present
PP5V_S4 - 0V missing
PM_PWRBTN_L - 3.40V always

Customer told it was working and shutdown the laptop. Few hours will not turn on anymore. No liquid damage.

title: [SOLVED]A1502 no power.
message: 3V on L7560? Check for short pulses on L7520. No auto ranging multimeter crap! Check all other rails for shorts.

message:

title: [SOLVED]A1502 no power.
message: I found missing 32KHZ and after replacing clock chip works. Problem solved.
